COMMUNITY LEADERSHIP
Investing in the Future 
We strive to embody the highest standards of honesty, integrity and client service while remaining mindful of our personal and corporate responsibility. Houlihan Lokey promotes community involvement, support and collaboration.
The Houlihan Lokey Charitable Giving Program was established to enhance our culture of charitable giving at all levels of the organization. We support a broad range of charitable activities and we dedicate our expertise and time to the advancement of the next generation of citizens through educational programs and personal and team volunteering. Our employees reach out and develop close community ties that make a positive impact. We also make contributions on behalf of our clients, assisting many local and national charities.
Corporate Giving Philosophy
Corporate responsibility is about a commitment to creating value for the client and helping meet societal needs. We are dedicated to promoting the economic, social and environmental well-being of the global communities in which we live and work. Our employees strive to honor this responsibility by contributing their time and energy to various causes.
In addition, we are dedicated to working with clients on strategic issues related to socially-minded business ventures. With offices throughout Europe, Asia and the United States, contributing to the global society is important to us. Our funding guidelines are aligned with our business and community needs.
Environment
We are committed to promoting sustainable and safe communities for our employees, clients and neighbors to help meet global and local environmental needs. To that end, we are dedicated to being environmentally responsible within each of our offices and within the communities in which we do business. 
We approach conserving natural resources and finding alternative uses for recyclable materials with the same vigor we approach finding innovative solutions to help our clients grow their businesses. As such, our recycling program is implemented company-wide.
Houlihan Lokey promotes the responsible use of energy throughout our business by encouraging carpooling, and is proactive about protecting and preserving our natural environment through our support of various organizations.
Education Initiative
Further expanding on our long-term goal to advance our clients’ vision through expert advice and personalized service, we are committed to preparing the next generation to help meet tomorrow’s business needs. Our education initiative is an integral part of who we are and what we do. Houlihan Lokey helps children by strengthening the foundation of their education. 
Give a Day to Charity
Houlihan Lokey strives for community collaboration and partnership through our Give a Day to Charity program. We believe that investing in the future starts by fortifying local bonds and promoting understanding. Employees are encouraged to combine their personal efforts by organizing team volunteering events for a charity of their choice.
Social Contributions
Houlihan Lokey promotes its aim of social responsibility through multi-faceted involvement, making charitable contributions in honor of clients and through charitable endeavors supported by our employees. As an embodiment of this commitment we sponsor various causes and events, some of the organizations to which we contribute include:

Make-a-Wish Foundation
National Center for Children & Families
The Leukemia & Lymphoma Society
Covenant House
Behind the Book
Second Harvest Food Bank
Youth, I.N.C.
Brooklyn Arts Exchange
UNICEF
Human Rights Watch
Horizons for Youth

Contribution Guidelines
Houlihan Lokey has an established process for accepting inquiries and proposals for contribution funding or charitable activities. We review requests on a case-by-case basis. 
 





















