OUR SERVICES
Delivering insight and expertise to help advance your vision
We guide clients through the complex financial and strategic challenges that they face during each stage of their business lifecycle. As a leading advisory-focused independent investment bank, we are able to serve as a trusted advocate to our clients across a number of key disciplines.
Corporate Finance
Ranked the No. 1 M&A advisor for all U.S. transactions by Thomson Reuters in 2016, Houlihan Lokey is also an active advisor in capital markets—with an international client base and a consistent track record of accomplishments.
Learn More 
Financial Advisory Services
Ranked the No.1 global M&A fairness opinion advisor by Thomson Reuters over the past 20 years, our depth of experience and intellectual rigor have made us a leading advisor on independent valuations and related financial advice worldwide.
Learn More 
Financial Restructuring
Our senior-level bankers are relentlessly dedicated to representing you in restructuring matters. In 2016, Thomson Reuters ranked Houlihan Lokey the No. 1 global investment banking restructuring advisor.
Learn More 
Strategic Consulting
Our experts deliver business expertise and in-depth knowledge in the areas of strategic development, operations, organization, and performance improvement to serve our large and mid-cap corporates and financial sponsors clients to unlock value for their companies.  
