Houlihan Lokey

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Houlihan Lokey, Inc.


Delivering insight and expertise to help advance your vision




Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: HLI


Industry
Investment banking


Founded
1972; 45 years ago (1972)


