Houlihan Lokey About To Put More Money In Your Pocket (HLI)
Looking at the universe of stocks we cover at Dividend Channel, on 5/31/17, Houlihan Lokey Inc will trade ex-dividend, for its quarterly dividend of $0.20, payable on 6/15/17. As a percentage of HLI's recent stock price of $33.42, this dividend works out to approximately 0.60%, so look for shares of Houlihan Lokey Inc to trade 0.60% lower — all else being equal — when HLI shares open for trading on 5/31/17.

May 30, 2017 10:25 AM EDT









